comments: Get the wheels up to speed
Wait for a bit so we don't mess with the shot
Wait for Frisbees to be in hopper
Wait for all shots to complete (assuming both will be shot in 3 seconds)
Drive forward 7 feet to pick up next two frisbees
Wait for Frisbees to be in hopper
Drive backward 7 feet while ramping up shooter and lowering spatula
Wait for all shots to complete
